title: Google Presents: Pixel Fall Launch
author: Made by Google
description:
Shop Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro beginning at 10 am PT: https://goo.gle/3FVoHXH

We’re officially introducing you to Pixel 6 and Pixel 6 Pro—the completely reimagined Google phones. Powered by Google Tensor, Google’s first custom mobile chip, they’re fast, smart and secure. And they adapt to you.
